<emphasis id="B950FE62045E3F158B838EDF980B3B96" bold="true" box="[151,316,1945,1970]" pageId="3" pageNumber="194">FIGURES 2–6.</emphasis>
Dorsal images of metasoma showing white spot pattern variations of male 
<taxonomicName id="4C2459F3045E3F158F598EDC9C343B95" box="[1101,1283,1946,1970]" class="Insecta" family="Pompilidae" genus="Abernessia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="194" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="prima">
